biography:
Akkana Peck is a freelance software developer and writer, and the author of the book &#8220;Beginning <span class="caps">GIMP</span>: From Novice to Professional.&#8221; 
She has been an open source software developer for some 20 years and has contributed to Mozilla, <span class="caps">GIMP</span> and an assortment of other projects.
